---
// StudioSection.astro
---

<section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#dcb0f7] to-[#aebef1] py-16 px-6 md:px-16 text-center md:text-left">
  
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-4">
    Our Studio Experience
  </h2>

  <p class="max-w-3xl text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed mb-8">
    FunGab Global is a UK-based creative powerhouse specializing in 
    <b>Media, Marketing, Photography, Music Production & Cinematography</b>. 
    Our studio blends innovation and visual storytelling to bring ideas to life 
    with precision, color and compelling impact.
  </p>

  <a 
    href="/services"
    class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-[#D234C7] to-[#32BEF1] hover:opacity-90 transition-all"
  >
    View Services
  </a>

</section>
